1783	### A13. HTTP Compression + Cache Headers (HIGH — addresses ISSUE-19, ISSUE-20)
1784	
1785	**Problem**: Plan targets "< 300KB gzipped" but never enables gzip. A3 adds X-headers but no Cache-Control.
1786	
1787	**1. Reverse Proxy Compression** (in nginx.conf — part of A4 Docker):
1788	```nginx
1789	# gzip for dynamic responses
1790	gzip on;
1791	gzip_types application/json text/plain text/css application/javascript;
1792	gzip_min_length 1024;
1793	gzip_comp_level 6;
1794	gzip_vary on;
1795	
1796	# brotli (if module available)
1797	brotli on;
1798	brotli_types application/json text/plain text/css application/javascript;
1799	brotli_comp_level 6;
1800	```
1801	
1802	**2. Vite Build-Time Precompression** (in vite.config.ts):
1803	```bash
1804	cd frontend && npm install vite-plugin-compression -D
1805	```
1806	```typescript
1807	import viteCompression from 'vite-plugin-compression';
1808	// In plugins array:
1809	viteCompression({ algorithm: 'gzip' }),
1810	viteCompression({ algorithm: 'brotliCompress', ext: '.br' }),
1811	```
