1958	> Write endpoints (bulk invoice generation, async exports, imports) are NOT throttled in this phase. After A10 observability is live, review telemetry for abuse patterns on mutation endpoints. If needed, add `api.write.heavy` limiter (e.g., 10 req/min for bulk-generate, 5 req/min for async exports). Do not hard-code now — enterprise bulk workflows must not be accidentally blocked.
