2027	### A17. Frontend Resilience — Error Boundaries + Service Worker (MEDIUM — addresses ISSUE-23, ISSUE-24)
2028	
2029	**1. Error Boundaries** (wrap every Suspense):
2030	```typescript
2031	// frontend/shared/components/ErrorBoundary.tsx
2032	class AppErrorBoundary extends React.Component<Props, State> {
2033	  state = { hasError: false, error: null };
2034	
2035	  static getDerivedStateFromError(error: Error) {
2036	    return { hasError: true, error };
2037	  }
2038	
2039	  componentDidCatch(error: Error, info: React.ErrorInfo) {
2040	    Sentry.captureException(error, { extra: info }); // Forward to A10
2041	  }
2042	
2043	  render() {
2044	    if (this.state.hasError) {
2045	      return (
2046	        <div className="p-8 text-center">
2047	          <p className="text-red-600">Đã xảy ra lỗi. Vui lòng tải lại trang.</p>
2048	          <button onClick={() => this.setState({ hasError: false })}>Thử lại</button>
2049	        </div>
2050	      );
2051	    }
2052	    return this.props.children;
2053	  }
2054	}
2055	
2056	// Usage pattern — wrap every React.lazy Suspense:
2057	<AppErrorBoundary>
2058	  <Suspense fallback={<LoadingSpinner />}>
2059	    <CustomerRequestHub />
2060	  </Suspense>
2061	</AppErrorBoundary>
2062	```
2063	
2064	**Placement rules**:
2065	- Route-level: each page/hub gets its own boundary
2066	- Modal-level: each lazy modal gets a boundary
2067	- Root-level: `AppErrorBoundary` in AppWithRouter.tsx as catch-all
2068	
2069	**2. Conservative Service Worker** (asset precache only):
2070	```bash
2071	cd frontend && npm install workbox-precaching workbox-routing -D
2072	```
2073	
2074	```typescript
2075	// frontend/sw.ts — precache build assets only, NO API caching
2076	import { precacheAndRoute, cleanupOutdatedCaches } from 'workbox-precaching';
2077	
2078	precacheAndRoute(self.__WB_MANIFEST); // Vite injects asset manifest
2079	cleanupOutdatedCaches();              // Clean old versions on deploy
2080	
2081	// NO runtime API caching — TanStack Query handles that
2082	// Kill switch: unregister SW via version flag
2083	self.addEventListener('message', (event) => {
2084	  if (event.data?.type === 'SKIP_WAITING') {
2085	    self.skipWaiting();
2086	  }
2087	});
2088	```
2089	
2090	**Kill Switch**: Set `VITE_SW_ENABLED=false` → skip SW registration in `index.tsx`.
2091	**Deploy Safety**: `cleanupOutdatedCaches()` + `skipWaiting()` ensures new deploy invalidates old SW cache.
2092	
